From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Codex <codex@openai.com>
Date: Tue, 16 Jun 2026 17:05:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] misc: initialize Fruit Jam usbhost EOP SM PC

Pico-PIO-USB initializes every state machine with pio_sm_init(), which
loads the initial program counter with a jmp to the program offset.  The
Fruit Jam bridge was doing that manually for TX and RX, but left the EOP
state machine at reset/stale PC while only programming its control
registers.

Jump the EOP state machine to the edge detector program before enabling it.
Also let the self-RX diagnostic release the initial RX_EOP wait before
transmitting so it can intentionally observe the host-driven packet.
---
 drivers/misc/fruitjam_usbhost.c | 3 +++
 1 file changed, 3 insertions(+)

diff --git a/drivers/misc/fruitjam_usbhost.c b/drivers/misc/fruitjam_usbhost.c
index 333333333333..444444444444 100644
--- a/drivers/misc/fruitjam_usbhost.c
+++ b/drivers/misc/fruitjam_usbhost.c
@@ -141,6 +141,7 @@
 #define FJ_PIO_RX_INIT_INSTR		(FJ_PIO_RX_OFFSET)
 #define FJ_PIO_RX_OSR_ONES_INSTR	0xa0ebu
 #define FJ_PIO_RX_SET_X_ZERO_INSTR	0xe020u
+#define FJ_PIO_EOP_INIT_INSTR		(FJ_PIO_EOP_OFFSET)
 #define FJ_PIO_INSTR_OP_MASK		0xe000u
 #define FJ_PIO_INSTR_JMP		0x0000u
 #define FJ_PIO_INSTR_ADDR_MASK		0x001fu
@@ -560,6 +561,7 @@
 	       FJ_PIO_EXECCTRL_WRAP_BOTTOM(FJ_PIO_EOP_WRAP_TARGET),
 	       eop_sm + FJ_PIO_SM_EXECCTRL);
 	writel(FJ_PIO_PINCTRL_IN_BASE(uh->dp_gpio), eop_sm + FJ_PIO_SM_PINCTRL);
+	writel(FJ_PIO_EOP_INIT_INSTR, eop_sm + FJ_PIO_SM_INSTR);
 
 	fj_usbhost_pio_sm_restart(uh, uh->sm_tx);
 	fj_usbhost_pio_sm_restart(uh, uh->sm_rx);
@@ -1070,6 +1072,7 @@
 		    ((token >> 8) & 0x7);
 
 	fj_usbhost_pio_prepare_receive(uh);
+	fj_usbhost_pio_clear_rx_irq(uh);
 	ret = fj_usbhost_pio_tx_packet(uh, packet, sizeof(packet),
 				       &encoded_len);
 	fj_usbhost_pio_record_tx(uh, ret, encoded_len);
